values:
Hey folks... 

I think I'm going to use this as a test bed for stories, ideas and such.. Most of the people who are on my friends list at this point are fellow writers, so I'm hoping you guys are paying attention to what I say... I doubt it, but I can hope *grin*

Ok, so, I'm working on the next Divergent Destinies story, which is the start of Xander's road trip, since I've actually got through Graduation written, albeit it not posted.  And I had an idea this morning... 

What do people think of Xander going by and seeing Jessie's parents before he leaves town?  I didn't have it planned originally, but it just strikes me as the kind of thing that he'd do... Or am I wrong here...

Ice
